OL,6,FA mass grave containing the bodies of
OL,7,Falmost 300 children and babies has
OL,8,Fbeen uncovered in a town's cemetery.
OL,10,FThe unmarked burial site in Royton
OL,11,FCemetery, Oldham, contains 145
OL,12,Fstillborn babies, 128 babies and young
OL,13,Fchildren and 29 adults, according to
OL,14,Flocal councillors.
OL,16,FRoyton Independent councillors Ms
OL,17,FHurley and Ms Hughes said they were
OL,18,F"profoundly affected" by the
OL,19,F"heartbreaking revelation".
