OL,4,C300 children and babies uncovered
OL,6,FThe discovery was made by a woman from
OL,7,Fthe local area who was searching for
OL,8,Fthe last resting place of her twin
OL,9,Fbrothers, who died in 1962.
OL,11,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,12,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,13,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,14,Four region.
OL,16,FBefore the 1980s, stillborns were
OL,17,Ftaken away from families and not given
OL,18,Fany details of where they were buried.
