OL,3,CMass grave containing bodies of almost
OL,4,C300 children and babies uncovered
OL,6,FMedical staff would tell bereaved
OL,7,Fparents their children would be buried
OL,8,Falongside "a nice person", but instead
OL,9,Fthe babies were laid to rest in mass
OL,10,Fgraves.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the councillors said:
OL,13,F"It's a stark injustice that parents
OL,14,Fwere denied the fundamental right to
OL,15,Fbury their babies, a right that should
OL,16,Fbe inherent and unquestionable.
OL,18,F"This situation should stir our
OL,19,Fcollective sense of fairness and
OL,20,Fempathy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
