OL,6,FA motion, due to be discussed at a
OL,7,Fcouncil meeting, has called for the
OL,8,Fcouncil to erect a memorial at the
OL,9,Fsite where the children, babies and
OL,10,Fadults are buried.
OL,12,FIt also suggests records and documents
OL,13,Fabout the burials should be made more
OL,14,Faccessible and digitalised.
OL,16,F"We cannot change what has happened",
OL,17,Fthe councillors added. "But we can
OL,18,Fensure that the babies born sleeping
OL,19,Fare named, recognised, and never
OL,20,Fforgotten."
