OL,6,FCllr Arooj Shah, Leader of Oldham
OL,7,FCouncil, said they will be "consider
OL,8,Fthe suggestion being made" with a
OL,9,F"matter of urgency", adding the grave
OL,10,Fis not "newly discovered".
OL,12,F"Our staff are here to support any
OL,13,Ffamilies who think they may be
OL,14,Faffected", he said.
OL,16,F"Sadly, the burying of people,
OL,17,Fincluding babies and children, in
OL,18,Funmarked graves happened in graveyards
OL,19,Fall around the country years ago.
