OL,4,C300 children and babies uncovered
OL,6,F"Thankfully, things have changed and
OL,7,Fimproved over the years. The
OL,8,FGovernment now pay for the funerals of
OL,9,Fstillborn babies and anyone up to the
OL,10,Fage of 18 if necessary. Public graves
OL,11,Fare no longer used.
OL,13,F"Today, when a request is made for
OL,14,Fburial in a public grave, the
OL,15,Farrangements are usually made by the
OL,16,Frelevant hospital via a funeral
OL,17,Fdirector. Often the hospital
OL,18,Fchaplaincy organises the burial or
OL,19,Fcremation of the individual.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
