OL,6,F"The council cemeteries staff also
OL,7,Fworks with the funeral director and
OL,8,Fcarry out the expressed wishes.
OL,10,F"The hospital and ourselves keep
OL,11,Frecords of the burial, which can be
OL,12,Flocated by families whenever they want.
OL,14,F"Alternatively, the family can make
OL,15,Ftheir own arrangements for burial in
OL,16,Fan individual grave plot via a funeral
OL,17,Fdirector and would install their own
OL,18,Fmemorial."
